Notes

	The hashing algorithm is a HASH160 which is a SHA256 followed by a RIPEMD160 hash - public key hash


	PublicKeyHash - Locking script
	1 P2WPKH : OP_0 OP_PUSHBYTES[20] 97cfc76442fe717f2a3f0cc9c175f7561b661997
	2 P2PKH  : OP_DUP OP_HASH160 OP_PUSHBYTES[20] 62e907b15cbf27d5425399ebf6f0fb50ebb88f18 OP_EQUALVERIFY OP_CHECKSIG
	3 P2SH   : OP_HASH160 OP_PUSHBYTES[20] 294410088c380ae01849dd8cff1f8f239ad2b3b6 OP_EQUAL

	OP_0 = 00
	OP_DUP = 76
	OP_HASH160 = a9
	OP_EQUALVERIFY = 88
	OP_CHECKSIG = ac
	OP_EQUAL = 87

	SHA256 operation twice on blockheader (hexadecimal) gives block hash (lesser than the difficulty)

